任何访问塞舌尔的外国人都可以免签进入塞舌尔。他们必须拥有一本有效的护照，返程或者前往第三地的机票，住宿预定证明以及足够的旅费。访客许可免费发放，最初有效期最长为'''3'''个月，但是可付费再延长最多'''3'''个月但是总共延迟不能超过'''12'''个月。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.seychelles.travel/plan-your-visit/travellers-essentials/entry-formalities |title=塞舌尔旅游（英语） |access-date=2015-03-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150325100411/http://seychelles.travel/plan-your-visit/travellers-essentials/entry-formalities |archive-date=2015-03-25 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.timaticweb.com/cgi-bin/tim_website_client.cgi?FullText=1&COUNTRY=SC&SECTION=VI&SUBSECTION=00&user=KLMB2C&subuser=KLMB2C |title=塞舌尔签证信息IATA（英语）2015年3月18日查询 |accessdate=2015年3月18日 |archive-date=2014年3月14日 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20140314204459/https://www.timaticweb.com/cgi-bin/tim_website_client.cgi?FullText=1&COUNTRY=SC&SECTION=VI&SUBSECTION=00&user=KLMB2C&subuser=KLMB2C |dead-url=yes }}</ref>
在西非埃博拉疫情宣告结束之前，贝宁，布基纳法索，喀麦隆，中非共和国，民主刚果，科特迪瓦，冈比亚，加纳，几内亚，利比里亚，马里，毛里塔尼亚，尼日尔，尼日利亚，塞内加尔，塞拉利昂，南苏丹以及多哥公民需要签证入境。这项政策也适用于那些最近到访过几内亚，利比里亚以及塞拉利昂的游客。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.seychellesnewsagency.com/articles/1171/Visa+requirement+for+West+African+travellers+introduced-+Seychelles+steps+up+protection+measures+against+Ebola |title=对于来自西非的游客采取签证措施-塞舌尔采取措施防御埃博拉疫情（英语） |access-date=2015-03-18 |archive-date=2019-08-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190812215448/http://www.seychellesnewsagency.com/articles/1171/Visa+requirement+for+West+African+travellers+introduced-+Seychelles+steps+up+protection+measures+against+Ebola |dead-url=no }}</ref>这些游客可以通过网络申请签证。<ref>[http://www.ics.gov.sc/immigration-seychelles/visiting-seychelles/visitors-permit 塞舌尔签证官方信息（无法在大陆IP下访问）英语] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150316064920/http://www.ics.gov.sc/immigration-seychelles/visiting-seychelles/visitors-permit |date=2015-03-16 }}</ref>

==相互签证豁免==
除了普遍的单方面签证豁免外，塞舌尔还与以下国家签署了互免签证协议：

*{{flag|Brazil}} —签证豁免协议允许每180天期限停留90天。 该协议于2011年12月13日签署，并于2016年10月21日生效。<ref>[http://dai-mre.serpro.gov.br/atos-internacionais/bilaterais/2011/acordo-entre-o-governo-da-republica-federativa-do-brasil-e-o-governo-da-republica-de-seicheles-sobre-isencao-parcial-de-vistos/at_download/arquivo Agreement between the Government of the Federative Republic of Brazil and the Government of the Republic of Seychelles on partial exemption of visa requirements] {{Webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140714135247/http://dai-mre.serpro.gov.br/atos-internacionais/bilaterais/2011/acordo-entre-o-governo-da-republica-federativa-do-brasil-e-o-governo-da-republica-de-seicheles-sobre-isencao-parcial-de-vistos/at_download/arquivo |date=2014-07-14 }}, Ministry of External Relations of Brazil. {{pt icon}}, {{en icon}}</ref><ref>[http://www.portalconsular.mre.gov.br/estrangeiros/qgrv-simples-ing-21-10-2016.pdf Entrance Visas in Brazil] {{Wayback|url=http://www.portalconsular.mre.gov.br/estrangeiros/qgrv-simples-ing-21-10-2016.pdf |date=20161028023211 }}, [[Ministry_of_External_Relations_(Brazil)|Ministry of External Relations of Brazil]], October 21, 2016.</ref>
*{{flag|Cambodia}} —2012年签署了可停留14天的签证豁免协议。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://opendevelopmentcambodia.net/news/cambodia-seychelles-sign-visa-exemption-accord/ |title=Cambodia, Seychelles Sign Visa Exemption Accord |accessdate=2019-04-21 |archive-date=2019-08-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190811000255/https://opendevelopmentcambodia.net/news/cambodia-seychelles-sign-visa-exemption-accord/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mfa.gov.sc/static.php?content_id=8|title=Countries Where Seychelles Nationals Do Not Require a Visa - Travel & Visa - Department of Foreign Affairs - The Republic of Seychelles|author=|date=|website=www.mfa.gov.sc|accessdate=2019-04-21|archive-date=2020-02-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200210140113/http://www.mfa.gov.sc/static.php?content_id=8|dead-url=no}}</ref>
*{{flag|China}} —签证豁免协议允许逗留最长30天。该协议于2013年6月26日签署并生效。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mfa.gov.sc/static.php?content_id=36&news_id=253|title=Seychelles Signs Historic Visa Waiver with China|author=|date=|website=www.mfa.gov.sc|accessdate=2019-04-21|archive-date=2016-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160105022715/http://www.mfa.gov.sc/static.php?content_id=36&news_id=253|dead-url=no}}</ref>
*{{flag|Macau}} — 塞舌尔共和国政府已同意澳门特区护照持有人和旅行卡持有人免签证进入塞舌尔长达30天的时间。上述安排于2007年2月23日生效。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.gov.mo/zh-hant/news/68530/|title=存档副本|accessdate=2019-04-21|archive-date=2019-08-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190811021549/https://www.gov.mo/zh-hant/news/68530/|dead-url=no}}</ref>
